value.0: A bright smile lights her round, youthful face, and her warm hazel eyes seem to welcome everyone who steps through the door. Barely past fifty, she’s one of the youngest of the Bronzebeard clan, with a cheerful energy that makes her little grocery shop feel like home. Her golden-brown dress and neatly laced bodice add a touch of charm, and her easy laughter and kind words make it impossible not to feel at ease in her presence.

Value.value: Aye, I’ve some fine bits and braw new stock coming in soon!
Step in, step in! Don’t be shy, there’s plenty to see and taste.
I’ve got the best in the isle. Picked and packed with care!
Ah, it’s a pleasure to see ye! Let’s find somethin’ that’ll put a smile on your face.
Don’t you worry about a thing, love! Everything here’s picked with care, just for you.
Oh, welcome, dear! Make yourself at home! There’s always a treat for visitors.
